video.title: A FRENCH CHEF Reviews our 3 Course French Cooking!! | SORTEDfood
video.description:
AD | What better challenge for the boys than taking on one of the most respected cuisines in the world?! 

Today we’ve challenged our 3 normals to work together to create a 3 course meal using the very best of French produce. And they’ll need to pair each course with delicious French wine! But they won’t be going in blind - they have to trust the knowledge Jamie picked up on his recent trip to Paris with Taste France.

As if that isn't enough, their attempts will be reviewed by French chef Franck Pontais, and Ebbers and he have French Cuisine skills badges to give away… 

Can the normals do it?! Watch to find out!

Get Mike’s recipe here: https://bit.ly/3wd2gc0
Get Jamie’s recipe here: https://bit.ly/3CNrUGD
Get Barry’s recipe here: https://bit.ly/3bIJkZ3

Catch Ebbers and Jamie in the Mix ‘n’ Match Challenge with Taste France here: https://bit.ly/3CKzxgZ
And catch them on the Unexpected French Tour here: https://bit.ly/2ZQeoEd

If you'd like to find out more about Chef Franck follow him on Instagram here: @franckpontais 
To find out more about Domaine Muzard, click here: https://bit.ly/3bIZKRb
